crew list as soon as you can.

370
00:33:26,837 --> 00:33:28,204
Certainly, sir.

371
00:33:28,237 --> 00:33:30,006
Patch me through to Lawrence Island...

372
00:33:30,039 --> 00:33:30,907
Yes, sir.

373
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,940
As soon as you can.

374
00:33:49,955 --> 00:33:51,757
