00:41:15,144 --> 00:41:16,245
What the hell was all that
shit about his father?

479
00:41:16,279 --> 00:41:18,279
I don't know.

480
00:41:26,153 --> 00:41:28,588
Christ, Captain, how did you spend 30

481
00:41:28,621 --> 00:41:30,621
