water's gotta be bad.

507
00:42:40,780 --> 00:42:42,780
Standing by.

508
00:42:49,219 --> 00:42:50,821
You copy, Flint?

509
00:42:50,854 --> 00:42:52,556
Start the broadcast.

510
00:42:52,589 --> 00:42:54,589
Broadcasting now.

511
00:43:01,730 --> 00:43:06,600
